|url=http://film-book.com/asian-film-awards-2012-nominations-the-flying-swords-of-dragon-gate/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=asian-film-awards-2012-nominations-the-flying-swords-of-dragon-gate
|publisher=Film Book
|title=Asian Film Awards 2012: Nominations: THE FLYING SWORDS OF DRAGON GATE
|date=January 18, 2012
|accessdate=January 30, 2012
|archive-date=2016-03-23
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323080805/http://film-book.com/asian-film-awards-2012-nominations-the-flying-swords-of-dragon-gate/?utm_campaign=asian-film-awards-2012-nominations-the-flying-swords-of-dragon-gate&utm_medium=rss&utm_source=rss
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。来自11个国家的32部电影获得本届提名<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/entertainment/2012-01/17/c_131365489.htm
|publisher=Xinhua Net
|title=Over 30 films nominated at 6th Asian Film Awards
|date=January 17, 2012
|accessdate=January 31, 2012
}}</ref>。其中《[[龙门飞甲|龙门飞甲]]》获得七项提名成为最多入围的电影。其次是《[[金陵十三钗|金陵十三钗]]》与《[[赛德克·巴莱|赛德克·巴莱]]》的六项提名；《[[伊朗式分居|伊朗式分居]]》与《[[武侠_(电影)|武侠]]》的四项提名。

《[[伊朗式分居|伊朗式分居]]》获得最佳电影、导演、编剧和剪辑四项大奖成为大赢家，而《[[武侠_(电影)|武侠]]》则获得最佳摄影、音乐和美术指导三个技术奖；[[许鞍华|许鞍华]]获得终身成就奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2012-03-19/19293584359.shtml |language= |title=第六届亚洲电影大奖获奖名单 |publisher=新浪 |date=2012年3月19日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2012-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323002512/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2012-03-19/19293584359.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

